lang="zh-CN">好吧，呃</span></p><p begin="30.522" end="31.388" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.522" end="30.624">If</span> <span begin="30.624" end="30.778">I</span> <span begin="30.778" end="30.861">was</span> <span begin="30.861" end="30.970">be</span><span begin="30.970" end="31.110">ing</span> <span begin="31.110" end="31.215">ho</span><span begin="31.215" end="31.388">nest</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那么，嗯，倘若坦诚而言</span></p><p begin="31.895" end="35.067" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.895" end="32.013">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="32.013" end="32.159">say</span> <span begin="32.159" end="32.289">long</span> <span begin="32.289" end="32.398">as</span> <span begin="32.398" end="32.564">I</span> <span begin="32.564" end="32.735">could</span> <span begin="32.735" end="32.888">fuck</span> <span begin="32.888" end="33.107">three</span> <span begin="33.107" end="33.277">times</span> <span begin="33.277" end="33.417">a</span> <span begin="33.417" end="33.583">day</span> <span begin="33.583" end="33.738">and</span> <span begin="33.738" end="33.920">not</span> <span begin="33.920" end="34.075">skip</span> <span begin="34.075" end="34.211">a</span> <span begin="34.211" end="34.443">meal</span> <span begin="34.443" end="34.646">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="34.646" end="35.067">good</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对我来说只要一天三次，食可饱腹就已满足</span></p><p begin="36.750" end="38.972" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.750" end="36.902">I</span> <span begin="36.902" end="37.025">used</span> <span begin="37.025" end="37.091">to</span> <span begin="37.091" end="37.206">work</span> <span begin="37.206" end="37.343">on</span> <span begin="37.343" end="37.504">my</span> <span begin="37.504" end="37.704">feet</span> <span begin="37.704" end="37.909">for</span> <span begin="37.909" end="38.070">se</span><span begin="38.070" end="38.194">ven</span> <span begin="38.194" end="38.314">dol</span><span begin="38.314" end="38.438">lars</span> <span begin="38.438" end="38.656">a</span> <span begin="38.656" end="38.781">ho</span><span begin="38.781" end="38.972">ur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是，我曾经为了一小时七美元的薪水拼命工作</span></p><p begin="38.972" end="40.089" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.972" end="39.110">Call</span> <span begin="39.110" end="39.264">my</span> <span begin="39.264" end="39.413">Ma</span><span begin="39.413" end="39.589">ma</span> <span begin="39.589" end="39.756">like,</span> <span begin="39.756" end="39.889">&quot;Ma</span><span begin="39.889" end="40.089">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">打电话给只为跟妈妈说</span></p><p begin="40.391" end="42.101" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.391" end="40.553">I</span> <span begin="40.553" end="40.723">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="40.723" end="40.832">ma</span><span begin="40.832" end="41.008">king</span> <span begin="41.008" end="41.126">mi</span><span begin="41.126" end="41.235">ni</span><span begin="41.235" end="41.425">mum</span> <span begin="41.425" end="41.702">wage,</span> <span begin="41.702" end="41.820">Ma</span><span begin="41.820" end="42.101">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我拿的不再是最低工资啦”</span></p><p begin="42.352" end="43.307" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.352" end="42.577">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="42.577" end="42.880">on,</span> <span begin="42.880" end="43.005">Ma</span><span begin="43.005" end="43.307">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我出息了妈妈”</span></p><p begin="43.493" end="43.983" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.493" end="43.598">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="43.598" end="43.983">on</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我有出息啦”</span></p><p begin="45.118" end="48.364" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.118" end="45.249">Now</span> <span begin="45.249" end="45.294">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="45.294" end="45.444">ma</span><span begin="45.444" end="45.557">king</span> <span begin="45.557" end="45.763">4</span> <span begin="45.763" end="45.916">hun</span><span begin="45.916" end="45.983">nid,</span> <span begin="46.410" end="46.608">6</span> <span begin="46.608" end="46.711">hun</span><span begin="46.711" end="46.874">nid,</span> <span begin="47.428" end="47.647">8</span> <span begin="47.647" end="47.759">hun</span><span begin="47.759" end="47.912">nid</span> <span begin="47.912" end="48.192">K,</span> <span begin="48.192" end="48.311">Ma</span><span begin="48.311" end="48.364">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而如今，我动辄收入四十，六十，八十万美元</span></p><p begin="48.364" end="49.651" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.364" end="48.436">To</span> <span begin="48.436" end="48.594">stand</span> <span begin="48.594" end="48.793">on</span> <span begin="48.793" end="49.014">my</span> <span begin="49.014" end="49.236">feet,</span> <span begin="49.236" end="49.402">Ma</span><span begin="49.402" end="49.651">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">早已独当一面</span></p><p begin="50.126" end="52.888" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.126" end="50.249">Play</span> <span begin="50.249" end="50.328">these</span> <span begin="50.328" end="50.658">songs,</span> <span begin="50.641" end="50.901">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="50.901" end="50.998">the</span><span begin="50.998" end="51.238">ra</span><span begin="51.238" end="51.510">py</span> <span begin="51.510" end="51.639">Ma</span><span begin="51.639" end="51.897">ma,</span> <span begin="51.892" end="51.985">they</span> <span begin="51.985" end="52.097">pay</span><span begin="52.097" end="52.307">ing</span> <span begin="52.307" end="52.627">me,</span> <span begin="52.627" end="52.733">Ma</span><span begin="52.733" end="52.888">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是将自己的的真情实感谱曲成歌，他们却予我厚禄妈妈</span></p><p begin="53.375" end="54.260" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.375" end="53.502">I</span> <span begin="53.502" end="53.572">should</span> <span begin="53.572" end="53.661">be</span> <span begin="53.661" end="53.737">pay</span><span begin="53.737" end="53.966">ing</span> <span begin="53.966" end="54.260">them&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其实应该由我回报他们</span></p><p begin="55.320" end="58.466" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.320" end="55.447">I</span> <span begin="55.447" end="55.553">should</span> <span begin="55.553" end="55.724">be</span> <span begin="55.724" end="55.825">pay</span><span begin="55.825" end="55.992">ing</span> <span begin="55.992" end="56.373">y&apos;all</span> <span begin="56.373" end="56.523">ho</span><span begin="56.523" end="56.867">nest</span> <span begin="56.867" end="57.038">to</span> <span begin="57.038" end="58.466">God</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我对天发誓，我才应该回报你们所有人呀</span></p><p begin="59.920" end="1:02.241" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.920" end="1:00.072">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:00.072" end="1:00.296">just</span> <span begin="1:00.296" end="1:00.444">a</span> <span begin="1:00.444" end="1:00.776">guy</span> <span begin="1:00.776" end="1:00.926">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:00.926" end="1:01.067">not</span> <span begin="1:01.067" end="1:01.220">a</span> <span begin="1:01.220" end="1:02.241">god</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而我只是个凡人并不是神明</span></p><p begin="1:02.241" end="1:06.307" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.241" end="1:02.362">Some</span><span begin="1:02.362" end="1:02.494">times</span> <span begin="1:02.494" end="1:02.756">I</span> <span begin="1:02.756" end="1:03.350">feel</span> <span begin="1:03.350" end="1:03.683">like</span> <span begin="1:03.683" end="1:03.873">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:03.873" end="1:04.064">a</span> <span begin="1:04.064" end="1:04.454">god</span> <span begin="1:04.454" end="1:04.547">but</span> <span begin="1:04.547" end="1:04.651"